Description: A comprehensive toolkit for B-cell and T-cell Repertoire Module 
    Identification and eXploration (VDJ-REMIX). This package provides 
    bioinformatics workflows for processing AIRR-seq data, identifying 
    co-expression or structural modules within repertoires, and exploring 
    their clinical and biological relevance.
